    {
      "id": "1442223382702592301",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2025-11-23T18:40:49.651+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "@RebelMike For some reason, netgen is thinking that flattening these cells will make a better match\n```\nFlattening instances of gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__mux2_2 in cell tt_um_MichaelBell_tinyQV (0) makes a better match\nFlattening instances of gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__mux2_2 in cell tt_um_MichaelBell_tinyQV (1) makes a better match\nFlattening instances of gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__aoi21_4 in cell tt_um_MichaelBell_tinyQV (0) makes a better match\nFlattening instances of gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__aoi21_4 in cell tt_um_MichaelBell_tinyQV (1) makes a better match\nFlattening instances of gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__nand2_1 in cell tt_um_MichaelBell_tinyQV (0) makes a better match\nFlattening instances of gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__nand2_1 in cell tt_um_MichaelBell_tinyQV (1) makes a better match\nFlattening instances of gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__nand2_4 in cell tt_um_MichaelBell_tinyQV (0) makes a better match\nFlattening instances of gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__nand2_4 in cell tt_um_MichaelBell_tinyQV (1) makes a better match\nFlattening instances of gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__oai21_2 in cell tt_um_MichaelBell_tinyQV (0) makes a better match\nFlattening instances of gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__oai21_2 in cell tt_um_MichaelBell_tinyQV (1) makes a better match\nFlattening instances of gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__oai21_4 in cell tt_um_MichaelBell_tinyQV (0) makes a better match\nFlattening instances of gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__oai21_4 in cell tt_um_MichaelBell_tinyQV (1) makes a better match\n```",
      "author": {
