      "timestamp": "2025-11-23T18:42:11.786+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "However, flattening the abstract lef views that don't contain any devices causes a device mismatch.\n```\ngf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__and3_4 (1)        |gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__and3_4 (1)\n(no matching element)                      |nfet_06v0 (12656->10959)\n(no matching element)                      |pfet_06v0 (12656->10745)\nNumber of devices: 17150 **Mismatch**      |Number of devices: 38854 **Mismatch**\nNumber of nets: 20323 **Mismatch**         |Number of nets: 28705 **Mismatch**        \n```",
      "author": {
        "id": "738396032295108721",
        "name": "bailey8889",
        "discriminator": "0000",
        "nickname": "bailey",
        "color": null,
        "isBot": false,
        "roles": [],
        "avatarUrl": "2025-11_media/0-EB806.png"
      },
