    },
    {
      "id": "1442224000649396441",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2025-11-23T18:43:16.981+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "As to why netgen wants to flatten those cells, there may be a clue in `62-magic-spiceextraction/magic-spiceextraction.log`\n```\nWarning: use i_peripherals.i_user_peri06.cordic_module.iter_stage.z\\[0\\]_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__dffq_1_Q_D_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__clkinv_1_ZN_I_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__oai211_1_ZN_B_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__oai221_1_ZN_A1_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__aoi21_1_ZN_A2_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__mux2_2_Z_I0_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__mux2_2_Z_I0_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__mux2_2_Z_I1_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__mux2_2_I0_Z_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__nand2_1_A2_ZN_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__oai21_1_B_ZN_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__mux2_2_I appears more than once in def!\nWarning: use i_peripherals.i_user_peri06.cordic_module.iter_stage.z\\[0\\]_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__dffq_1_Q_D_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__clkinv_1_ZN_I_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__oai211_1_ZN_B_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__oai221_1_ZN_A1_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__aoi21_1_ZN_A2_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__mux2_2_Z_I1_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__mux2_2_Z_I1_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__mux2_2_Z_I1_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__mux2_2_I0_Z_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__nand2_1_A2_ZN_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__oai21_1_B_ZN_gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__oai21_1_ appears more than once in def!\n...\n```",
